Recruiter Comment: We are on the look out for an IT Infrastructure Engineer to be responsible for designing and setting up the IT infrastructure within a business enterprise for BPO. #Singapore #Jobs #CCNA #MCSE
Share:Job DescriptionIT Infrastructure Engineer is responsible for designing and setting up the IT infratructure within a business enterprise. He/She inspects the hardware components of the IT infrastructure and troubleshoots the network/ system in case of any problem. He/She is also responsible for providing updated infrastructure solutions for the organization keeping in mind the budget proposed.ResponsibilitiesDesign Configuration for IT infrastructure network and supervise its implementationIdentify business requirements and deliver cost-effective infrastructure solutions to the organizationMonitor systems, networks, and send assessment reports from time to time to the seniors/ managementUpdate the knowledge on recent developments in IT Infrastructure and apply it to company's network as per the organization's needsRevise and modify systems to ensure security within network environmentRequirementsBachelor's degree in IT with minimum 3 years experience in managing Data centre and enterprise network.CCNA and MCSE are preferredFamiliar with Linux, C, C++ and Java ScriptsUnderstanding of contractual languageProject management certifiedProblem solving skills demonstrated to identify and resolve critical issuesWeb, database and reports related developments experience especially using Microsoft .NET technologies.1 years experience operating in an international environmentAbility to work independently“Can do” attitudeGood understanding of information security Please send your resume in WORD format to  or contact Yvonne Tan on +65 6332 0138 for a confidential discussion. Please note that only short-listed candidates will be contacted.ProfileYour IT Trained Recruiter
